On following code, we are not generating the proper variable entry in local 
variable attribute:

public class X {
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		int i;	
		outer: {
			if (args == null) {
				i = 0;
				break outer;
			}
			return;
		}
		System.out.println(i);	// no entry in var attribute
	}
}

